73
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:10,510
<i>To jsi tu sám? </i>

74
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,990
<i>Chápu. </i>

75
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,030
<i>Tak to jsme na tom stejně. </i>

76
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:18,750
<i>Pojď se mnou. </i>

77
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:22,190
<i>Ode dneška budeme my dva spolu. </i>

78
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:26,880
Proč, Ginjo?

79
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:30,970
